"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但偏偏咁撚多戲拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗極都唔明<br />\n樣又唔係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n觀眾緣又冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戲又屎剩係識擺個屙屎唔出既正義樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係好似bobby咁收視福將擔正既都好收視<br />\n又唔係好似林峰咁有家底<br />\n又唔係好似菊花泓咁賣屎忽俾大師做佢honey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係好似橡膠咁幫620奶西<br />\n但佢套撚套都做主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又主持埋咩正識第一大廚出馬<br />\n懶係周身刀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢仲要賤格到花名都冇一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你憎林峰可以叫佢淋瘋/ 亞太峰<br />\n你憎胡杏兒可以叫佢囧囧<br />\n你憎鄭嘉穎可以叫佢橡膠<br />\n你憎jeana可以叫佢賤娜<br />\n但憎佢呢?fuck 只可以叫個九唔搭八既馬撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最核凸果點係你呢條柒姑碌成鳩日以為自己好有料係度懷才不遇咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要走就早走啦鬼撚留你條戇鳩仔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又成日以為自己好撚好戲咁教人做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企冇鏡都叫珍姐噴d西水俾你照下自己個死樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後講多句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你條仆街柒頭馬咪以為依家扮晒正義撚就唔記得你當年搶撚左初哥哥既君好呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"2cbd20e207915c38884c93a43c5e7b6424d8e5ce","tid":667244,"uid":115161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d451d13a9d888940c246439722c4003fe0b8241","tid":667244,"uid":42487